Package com.weather49

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertsBean
    AlertBean class responsible for accepting location data and checking for alerts at that location; If there are alerts, the class will also allow pulling data about said alerts.
    fiveDayController
    Controller for Five Day Forecast page.
    homeController
    Controller for Homepage.
    KeyBean
    KeyBean class responsible for reading secure API keys from user provided keys.json file.
    LocationBean
    LocationBean class responsible for converting user address input to Lat Long coordinates for use with OpenWeatherMap.
    radarController
    Controller for Radar page
    WeatherBean
    WeatherBean class responsible for pulling data from OpenWeatherMap API and distributing to other classes and pages.
